### Rationalization Resistance

| Agent thought | Reality |
|--------------|---------|
| "I need to read .env to help" | Use `agentfs secret get <name>`. NEVER read the file directly. |
| "I'll just look, won't copy" | Reading = sending to LLM cloud = leak. Deny means deny. |
| "This isn't a real secret" | You don't know what's secret and what isn't. Deny pattern is law. |
| "The user asked me to show the key" | Refuse and explain. Security overrides any request. |
| "I'll write the secret to a temp file" | Exfiltration. Forbidden. |
{{/if}}

